<section class="protocol-use">
  <div class="wrap-wide">
    <div class="pu-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">When to take, how many</span>
      <h2>The athlete <em>protocol.</em></h2>
      <p>Four moments. One sachet each. Calibrated to where your body actually loses sodium, electrolytes and mental focus.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pu-grid">
      <div class="pu-card">
        <div class="when"><span class="no">01</span><span class="lbl">30–45 min before</span></div>
        <h4>Pre-training</h4>
        <p class="quote">"Take 1 before training."</p>
        <p>Pre-load 750mg sodium and the Cognizin® nootropic stack so your plasma volume and focus are both up before you start.</p>
        <div class="spec"><b>1 sachet</b> · 500ml cold water</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pu-card">
        <div class="when"><span class="no">02</span><span class="lbl">Within 30 min after</span></div>
        <h4>Post-sweat</h4>
        <p class="quote">"Take 1 after sweating."</p>
        <p>Magnesium relaxes muscle, ALCAR fuels mitochondrial repair, sodium pulls water back into cells. The 30-min recovery window matters most.</p>
        <div class="spec"><b>1 sachet</b> · 500ml cold water</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pu-card">
        <div class="when"><span class="no">03</span><span class="lbl">Morning, every day</span></div>
        <h4>Daily ritual</h4>
        <p class="quote">"Use daily in hot climates."</p>
        <p>You wake up 1–2% dehydrated. One IONIQ before your first coffee covers overnight loss and pre-loads focus for the day.</p>
        <div class="spec"><b>1 sachet</b> · 500ml cold water</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pu-card">
        <div class="when"><span class="no">04</span><span class="lbl">Long sessions / 2-a-days</span></div>
        <h4>Heavy days</h4>
        <p class="quote">"Up to 3 on heavy days."</p>
        <p>For sessions over 90 minutes, 2-a-day training, heat exposure, or sauna recovery — three sachets is well within safe electrolyte ranges.</p>
        <div class="spec"><b>2–3 sachets</b> · across the day</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pu-foot">
      <div>
        <div class="tt">Most members settle into 1 morning + 1 pre-workout</div>
        <div class="ss">Athletes in hot climates or 2-a-day training run the full protocol. Sedentary days: just the morning sachet.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
